    "description": {
      "zh": "诺文斯基核动力金牌格瓦斯。作为一种传统的斯拉夫饮料，它不仅是一种美味，而且是一种健康的产品。这是因为在俄罗斯的传说中，斯拉夫勇士为了重新变得爷们，经常喝这玩意。",
      "en": "Norvinsky Premium, a truly refreshing kvass. Kvass is made by the natural fermentation of bread, such as wheat, rye, or barley, and sometimes flavoured using fruit, berries, raisins, or birch sap. One of the traditional Slavic drinks, it is not just a tasty, but also a healthy product. It is for a reason that in Russian tales it is constantly drunk by Bogatyrs to regain their power."
    },
